First of all, a snob is someone who completely dismisses any kind of constructive criticism (such as grammar and spelling) because he or she is so self-righteous that they're incapable of realizing when they're wrong.  Second of all, I hate to break it to you pal, but we're judging the BOOK by the BOOK.  There is no cover here, it's an online forum and the only thing we have to base our opinions on is CONTENT.<br>
<br>
